{"tid":657354,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"古代人個個都係讀中文","createTime":"2018-05-08T04:37:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T16:39:31.000Z","uid":35324,"like":26,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a542375fbae5446ddf299617cf629ea983f1815d","tid":657354,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T04:37:57.000Z","msg":"舊時冇英文，冇數學，冇science，更莫講話business、finance<br />\n個個要考科舉，都只係讀中文，背晒四書五經，再自己寫下文、發表下議論<br />\n<br />\n而家所謂嘅law同政政，舊時都係啲讀中文嘅人up出嚟，朝廷上嘅大臣全部靠讀中文上位<br />\n所謂嘅philo都係嗰堆文人寫文做埋哲學家<br />\n以前想成功就係讀中文然後升官發財（或者可以練武功做大將軍）<br />\n<br />\n但而家讀中文已淪為乞食科<br />\ndse雞個個都唔想考中文，話係死亡之卷，搞到佢地2咗入唔到u<br />\n入到u更加冇人揀中文，你揀咗仲會比親戚朋友百般質疑：吓，咁你第日做咩呀<br />\n<br />\n原來世界真的變了好多"},{"pid":"8ec2636aa5ce89bea341336ac32f52897774f832","tid":657354,"uid":7837,"like":16,"dislike":6,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T04:38:51.000Z","msg":"返古代囉你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf7dcb19482e85d7f0394ce7d8ad91a74bce351","tid":657354,"uid":35324,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8ec2636aa5ce89bea341336ac32f52897774f832","tid":657354,"uid":7837,"like":16,"dislike":6,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T04:38:51.000Z","msg":"返古代囉你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T04:40:06.000Z","msg":"你唔係應該好十卜中文咩 yy lam"},{"pid":"f4c2e3e561cd6e2154aa9383753139b0eef6e21b","tid":657354,"uid":3775,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T04:40:43.000Z","msg":"講真 <br />\n<br />\n中文就無乜野 語言一種<br />\n<br />\n不過古代文人正仆街係就真 理得佢幾好文彩都咁話<br />\n<br />\n尤其萬般皆下品，惟有讀書高 垃圾思想主導"},{"pid":"a907bae167e263e9f98b76838bcc87a2c3fc5e97","tid":657354,"uid":7837,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"2cf7dcb19482e85d7f0394ce7d8ad91a74bce351","tid":657354,"uid":35324,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8ec2636aa5ce89bea341336ac32f52897774f832","tid":657354,"uid":7837,"like":16,"dislike":6,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTim